snippet.title: Diana plays at the Supermarket and doing Shopping with Baby Doll
snippet.description:
Diana plays at the Supermarket in Thailand. Great Supermarket with lots of Children Activities and fun kids toys! Diana's family had fun playing with learning toys and pretend food. Roma and Diana also doing Shopping with Baby Doll. Fun Kids Video for children who loves playing with toys
